{"tid":2162210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"飯民家陣道理講唔過，開始情緒綁架，咩不分化不割蓆原則出哂來","createTime":"2020-08-18T04:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T04:10:55.000Z","uid":63361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"907f1fcf93b3f02e78b870fccae007950bba12b0","tid":2162210,"uid":63361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，社運無限loop<br />\n<br />\n做7野/賣香港 ＞選舉個陣就打告急牌/話要堅守民主自由，強調議會抗爭先係主要出路＞香港人含淚投飯民＞飯人民做7野/賣香港＞再loop以上程序<br />\n<br />\n道德綁架主要係用來綁住自己而唔會綁到飯民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番過去一年，做到野既得勇武，gphone個班搞國際線做backup，飯民就去美國叫人唔好制裁倒米。唉，我都唔再數，連登仔，醒喇。"},{"pid":"25e64555b13ad5de5c12847e26c113b922813174","tid":2162210,"uid":63361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:10:55.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"}]}